column2: SELECT m.id as [id], str (m.ra, #, #) AS ra, str (m.dec, #, #) AS dec, n.distance, sp.ra AS ra2, sp.dec AS dec2, po.plate, po.mjd, po.fiberid, str (po.z, #, #) as spec_z into MyDB.out_#K_polarBAL_dr9 from MyDB.cas_input_#K_polar AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS sp ON n.objid = sp.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS po ON po.objID = sp.objID LEFT OUTER JOIN photoZ pp ON pp.objID = sp.objID
